Adding the Title and Logo 10
  • Create the Title
          1) Click on the "Text Box" Button on the ribbon to add a text box to the report

             Go to General and write  1197 on Width and 44 on Height

               Go to Title and on the title text box type Sales Dashboard

               Change the background Pupple #573b92

               Chose Text size to 24 and Segoe UI Bold then center it

 Add Colaberry Logo

-                     Go to Insert tab and click on Image

-                     Browse the Colabery Logo if you saved it on your computer

-                    Adjust the size and fit it at the left side of the Title box
